- **NVDA below $207.41 on heavy volume for 2 straight days** — This is the intermediate support line; if it breaks on conviction, the entire demand anchor thesis is broken and the portfolio cascades down.
- **Next hyperscaler earnings (Microsoft, Google, Meta, Amazon) shows CapEx slowing or pausing, not accelerating** — This kills the foundational assumption that all four agents are trading; if growth is flat or down, SMH, LITE, TSM, and AVGO all drawdown simultaneously.
