- **The single most important signal: next hyperscaler earnings commentary on CapEx guidance and whether they cite permitting delays, power grid constraints, or political backlash as reasons to moderate growth** — This is the thesis-integrity test.
- **Where to look: Microsoft, Google, Meta, Amazon earnings calls (next 2-3 weeks); listen for any mention of "data center permitting," "power grid constraints," "municipal delays," or "infrastructure bottlenecks"** — If any hyperscaler cites infrastructure as a constraint, the semiconductor thesis collapses.
